The steps below can all be executed by running setup.sh
If run without sudo, the last step will fail and not install anything.

To clean up the repository, use clean.sh

To generate the ./configure script, execute the following commands:

$ autoreconf -i
$ aclocal
$ automake --add-missing
$ autoconf

To build and install the program, execute the following commands:

$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install
